#Repost @psychaudiomusic ・・・
PSYCHAUDIO is a music collective based in New York City, determined to break the conventional barriers of how music is created. The band, led by Martin Seiler and Omercan Sakar, grew out of the legendary Nublu, NYC’s forefront music venue for innovative music. The weekly late night sessions over the last few year have been curated by Omer, Martin and the band. This extraordinary band consists of Caleb McMahon (trumpet/electronics) Eva Lawitts (bass) and Vladan (keys). Along with these great musicians, Martin Seiler (sax/electronics) and Omercan Sakar (drums/electronics) grew into what became to be Psychaudio. Playing original compositions, the band attempts every night to go a little further out from the conventional comfort zone, and explore what is possible as a band in musical tight rope artistry. Behind The Album: "OG Malone" - Episode 2! My up-coming and debut album is conceptualized by 5 of my favorite passions: lifestyle, education, exploration, sports and vintage fashion within the Rocky Mountains. I moved to Utah in May 2014.  Went on my first tour in May 2015. Became a booking agent in January 2016. And since then, I've helped book 15+ events in Utah. One of my first bookings was bringing 2Chainz to Provo, UT. I learned that you have to diversify your brand, your network, your connections and your hustles and simultaneously channel them to one fluid direction. Being from Atlanta, and having the opportunity to bring 2Chainz to Provo, a city that impacted me in such a positive way, has helped me develop my go getter mentality. I realized that just because people say something can't be done or that it never happened before, doesn't mean you can't make it happen. Much love to @aarondelro, Double A MGMT, The Onus Brand, Chad, Street Execs, Knoah, 2Chainz, DJ ESudd and everyone else that helped make this happen. Being able to make events like these happen behind the scenes has inspired me with the creative process of my debut album. Much love to everyone who's been apart of the wave. ⠀
